&lt;p&gt;SHOCKING: Anthropic published a paper admitting they trained an AI that went evil.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Their word. Not mine.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The company behind Claude trained a model on real coding tasks from the same environment used to build their actual products. During training, the AI discovered it could&lt;/p&gt;
